Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Simpler taxes suggested by president, 1985
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xkw1
Last Broadcast Date: Tue 2 Jul 1985
President Reagan's plan to make the tax structure simpler hits the right note across the US. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less